Bronzong (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0436: Bronzor
Pokémon
#0438: Bonsly →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Bronzong (TCG Pocket).

Bronzong has been featured on 25 different cards since it debuted in the Mysterious Treasures expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Bronzong cards are normally Metal-type or Psychic-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Bronzong

Bronzong
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
